fields.name: Solo Dance
fields.about: If you think your moves can shake the stage and make the audience groove, then it’s time you put your best foot forward and participate in Stag Moves, the solo-dancing competition. The competition will be amongst the best groovers from colleges from around the country.

fields.name: Duet Dance
fields.about: It’s time to partner up and show your camaraderie to the audience and the judges. Fear not, the competition though tough can be won by showcasing your dance skills, groove, and rhythm. And never forget anybody can duet!

fields.name: Street Battle
fields.about: A war with no blood but the sweat of your hard work, moves, and music. Though no harm will be inflicted upon you the wounds will be deep. Get your shoes all tied up and leave no laces untied coz no one will be spared in this battle of streets. It’s time to rock the spot!

fields.name: Solo Singing
fields.about: Every sound is made by harmonizing various frequencies. And it is a perfect combination of harmonies that makes you a winner of this competition of Solo-singing. Do you think you have the talent to charm the audience? If yes, then register for Aria, the solo-singing competition!

fields.name: Duet Singing
fields.about: It’s time to team up and get your chords right. The competition to show your unity in your voice and in melodies is here. Duetto, the duet-singing competition, sees one of the most beautiful vocalists from around the country.

fields.name: RAP
fields.about: A solo competition where each participant will be allowed only to sing a rap. Rap is the art of delivering popular music vocally in a way that mixes rhyme, rhythmic speech, and ghetto slang. It is going to be fierce !! This is your chance to perform in front of a large audience if you believe you are capable of expressing emotions via rap. Leverage the power of the chance now and showcase your talent.

fields.name: General Quiz
fields.about: Life is not Finals, it's a collection of daily pop quizzes. So why not have a quiz competition where you can utilize all of your enormous knowledge from your everyday life pop quizzes to impress everyone that you can completely master the event? Here’s your chance to roll the dice and put everything on the line for this quiz.

fields.name: MELA Quiz
fields.about: Music, entertainment, literature, and art. The questions range from the beginning to the end. Find a team that will cover all those genres and see how you stack up against the other teams. Nobody can stop you from winning the contest if you feel you are skilled in all specified categories. Gather all of your excitement and let it all out.

fields.name: Multiple Fandom Quiz
fields.about: Do you consider yourself a movie and literature buff? Putting your brain on display in front of fellow competitors on your favorite subject would be nothing but joy. All you need for this quiz is your childish and exuberant side. But don't let your childlike side forget the pen while participating.

fields.name: Mono Acting
fields.about: Do you think you have the capability to make a room full of scrutinizing audiences laugh, cry, or be angry? Then, the stage of Ekalnatya is all yours and yours only to put your acting talent to the test. It’s a competition where you show off your acting skills, your bravery, and how well you can capture the audience and stir a bucket of emotions in them.

fields.name: Funky Faces
fields.about: What better canvas than a human face? It’s time to gather your paints, brushes, and ideas to paint a painting on a face. Funky Face is a face-painting competition full of colors and creativity that will add a fun hue to the fest of IGNUS.

fields.name: ArTees
fields.about: Creativity is subjective to every individual. A T-shirt is like a blank canvas that can be made into a fashion statement of your own. Fashion is ever-evolving and so can your design. ArTees is a T-shirt painting competition to showcase your creativity and brilliance.

fields.name: Charcoal Painting
fields.about: Charcoal is one of the most conventional art forms practiced with drawing sketches. The world can be seen in monochrome just like in old films and charcoal painting is a way to bring the visuals to a canvas.

fields.name: Live Sketching
fields.about: Sketching is the artist’s spontaneous expression of what his eyes are onlooking at. A sketch represents an artist’s personality and perspective. Live sketching is a competition where artists are free to voice their thoughts through their artworks.

fields.name: Doodling
fields.about: Anything and everything can be doodled is a doodler’s motivation. A doodle can either have a concrete representational meaning or can be composed of random and abstract lines or shapes. A doodling competition is a perfect place for all the maestros or amateurs to express their artistry.

fields.name: Rapido
fields.about: They say that practice makes perfect. However, now witness a game in which sketching the same object becomes tougher and tougher. Speed and accuracy are definitely the skills that you will require to win this.

fields.name: Wordzee
fields.about: They say the time to relax is when you don't have time for it. So if you want to have your mind relaxed during a hectic festival then come and join us in a fun session with your friends.

fields.name: Extempore
fields.about: A ready-made speech is a dead lion. An extempore speech is a live cat. The latter connects you with an audience. The former distracts their attention. So If you believe you can think on your feet then come and join us in an engaging extempore competition.

fields.name: Pun Wars
fields.about: A truly good pun is its own “reword”. Puns are spontaneous reactions to situations that bring forth your creative and hilarious sides. What better opportunity can you get to use all your best pj’s and dad jokes?

fields.name: JAM
fields.about: A ready-made speech is a dead lion. An extempore speech is a live cat. The latter connects you with an audience. The former distracts their attention. So If you believe you can think on your feet then come and join us in an engaging extempore competition.

fields.name: STEW
fields.about: With your head full of brains and your shoes full of feet, you should be too smart to go down. So if you think you have what it takes, we invite you to a gathering of the brightest and the wittiest minds where you will compete in a series of eccentric events to find out who is the smartest of all.

fields.name: Photography in IITJ
fields.about: Photography, as we all know, is an illusion of reality with which we create our own private world of memories. When the world asks, "What was it like?" Only the photographer can say, "See! I can show you". The art of photography allows us to capture memorable moments and every small detail that we otherwise might forget. So get your cameras and capture the moments.

fields.name: IGnify
fields.about: Reels have unquestionably evolved in this digital age into a platform for the younger generation to showcase their creativity and introduce the best social media trends. If you think you’ve mastered that creativity of syncing your actions to the beats and if you think there’s no one that can beat you in this, then stop beating around the bush and enter the real competition.

fields.name: Lollapalooza
fields.about:
Are memes your second language?
Do Harambe, LOLcats, squinting fry, evil Kermit, "choti Bacchi ho kya", Baburao, and chai pilo.. make more sense to you than anything else in this world?
"Kabhi kabhi lagta hai na ki apun hi bhagwaan h?" aur baaki "sab doglapan h"?
Well, then this could be your chance to shine!

fields.name: Photography
fields.about: Photography, as we all know, is an illusion of reality with which we create our own private world of memories. When the world asks, "What was it like?” Only a photographer can say, “See! I can show you”.The art of photography allows us to capture memorable moments and every small detail that we otherwise might forget. So get your cameras and capture the moments.

fields.name: Short Movie Making
fields.about:
Do you have a story to tell? Do you make videos?  
If film-making is what keeps you up at night, here we are with our invigorating Short Film-Making contest! It doesn't matter where you come from or who you are, you can unite lives with your story. So if you can challenge yourself to create big things in a short time, now's your chance.

fields.name: Dubsmash
fields.about: We would welcome you to join us for the most captivating Dubsmash competition. Join us because we know that you can always perform better than you think, for you are an amalgamation of all talent and creativity. Now is the time to thread all your on-camera skills which might surprise everyone.

fields.name: Creative Writing
fields.about:
"Writers are dangerous people. They know to aim with sentences, how to fire with paragraphs, and how to immortalize their kills in verse."

If words flow inside you like water, and you are overwhelmed with the insatiable desire to write, then join us for the most challenging Creative Writing competition and showcase your gift of turning blood into ink.

fields.name: Digital Art
fields.about: Digital Art is just like painting, except the paint, never dries up. Join us in the event and prove that digital art empowers both the painterly side of photographers and the photographer side of painters.

fields.name: Photoshop Battle
fields.about:
Do you think you can make a better spiderman poster than MARVEL? Do you have a way with lighting and contrast and photoshop brushes? 
Well, we invite you to immerse yourself in all the photographic awesomeness! Take this chance to try your hand at our Photoshop contest and show off your creativity and technical abilities! You will be up against the best and that’s the best way to learn.

fields.name: Fashion Show (Antarang)
fields.about: Antarang, the flagship Fashion Show of IGNUS witnesses a multitude of styles, and elegant and astounding talent in fashion design from participants across the country. With exciting prizes, the show is judged by India’s top fashion icons who have won Beauty Pageants. So, if you think your costumes have the pizzazz to compete, then be quick to register.

fields.name: Group Dance (Nrityansh)
fields.about: Nrityansh, the flagship event of IGNUS is the hypnotic and wild group dance competition where the dance troops from all over the country assemble and face off against each other. The competition is judged by India’s top choreographers and dancers who have been in the big leagues of the dance world.

fields.name: Aayaam (Nukkad)
fields.about: Aayaam is the street-play competition where myriad top colleges of India compete to narrate Social Issues through raw emotions out on the ground. A competition so fierce, raw, and heart-wrenching that has never been seen before.

fields.name: Clash of Bands
fields.about: The beats that can make the audience melancholy and frantic are what we are looking for in Thunderbeats, the Clash of Bands competition.  A feral competition with teams clashing with each other with their instruments, beats, and thrills. And bonus points for using a Bohemian instrument!
